00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.700
Pricing Is Paramount – The
Impact of Proper Pricing

00:00:03.337 --> 00:00:07.207
Pricing your home correctly has a direct
impact on how buyers respond to it.

00:00:09.040 --> 00:00:11.719
When your home is priced in line
with the market, it attracts

00:00:11.719 --> 00:00:13.250
serious, qualified buyers.

00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:16.989
These are buyers who are ready,
willing, and able to make an offer.

00:00:17.599 --> 00:00:20.950
Proper pricing creates more
online views, more showings, and

00:00:20.950 --> 00:00:22.380
more real interest in your home.

00:00:23.725 --> 00:00:27.395
It can be tempting to price higher
and plan to negotiate down, but

00:00:27.395 --> 00:00:28.884
that often works against you.

00:00:29.534 --> 00:00:32.785
Homes that are overpriced tend
to sit on the market longer.

00:00:33.164 --> 00:00:37.004
As time passes, buyers don’t
just question the value, but

00:00:37.004 --> 00:00:39.954
they also may begin to wonder if
something is wrong with the home.

00:00:40.655 --> 00:00:44.245
This loss of confidence often
leads to price reductions and

00:00:44.245 --> 00:00:45.925
a lower final sales price.

00:00:46.700 --> 00:00:48.609
A well-priced home creates urgency.

00:00:48.660 --> 00:00:52.480
It can lead to multiple offers,
stronger terms, and a faster sale.

00:00:53.162 --> 00:00:55.082
Pricing is not about guessing high.

00:00:55.742 --> 00:00:58.512
The longer a home sits on
the market, the more buyers

00:00:58.512 --> 00:01:00.292
expect to pay less than asking.

00:01:00.802 --> 00:01:04.312
Strategic pricing positions your
home to attract strong offers

00:01:04.522 --> 00:01:05.842
and win in today’s market.

